sent.orig: DST (Drill Stem Test), a fast test for show of oil and gas while drilling.

sent.orig: This is a summary report of the development of CHANGSHA norms of Benton vis-ral Retention Test(VRT).
sent.trans: 本文是 Benton 视觉保持测验(Visual Retention Test,简称 VRT)长沙常模制订及试测总结。

sent.orig: The result was analyzed statistically by X2 (chi-square test) to compare the difference between two nationalities.
